\par }\pard \qj {\f30\fs28 
\par }\pard \qj {\b\f32\fs28 XSSCRATCH }{\f30\fs28 : The directory name where temporary files will be kept.
\par }\pard \qj {\f30\fs28 
\par }\pard \qj {\b\f32\fs28 XSINPUTFILES}{\f30\fs28  : The directory name where your standard Columbia University's Switcap input files will be stored.
\par }\pard \qj {\f30\fs28 
\par }\pard \qj {\b\f32\fs28 XSOUTPUTFILES}{\f30\fs28  : The directory name where your standard Columbia University's Switcap output files will be stored.
